From misc. sources (with good licenses):
----------------------------------------

From olpc-sound-samples-v2, CC AT 3.0:
computer.wav      Berklee44v7/computer_mania2.wav
doorOpen.wav      Berklee44v10/door_hangar1.wav
tankBeam.wav      Berklee44v13/synth_laser4.wav
tankBeamFire.wav  Berklee44v13/laser_2.wav
waterIn.wav       Berklee44v10/water_plunge1.wav
                  (only the first part)

Made by Hans de Goede, CC AT 3.0:
droid1.wav        Made in sfxr, can be opened in sfxr by opening droid1.sfxr
droid2.wav        Made in sfxr, can be opened in sfxr by opening droid2.sfxr
elecDeath1.wav    explo1.sfxr + last part of
                  http://soundbible.com/1276-Robot-Computing.html
                  By: Mike Koenig
elecDeath2.wav    explo1.sfxr + a part of Berklee44v13/synth_computer_fax3.wav
Note: The sfxr files were made with sfxr on a x86_64 machine and the .sfxr
format is likely arch dependent.

Unmodified from original blobwars:
Lock And Load!!!  Short voice sample from move, fair use

Copies of other sound effects
droidChangeFreq.wav Copy of droid1.wav (just like with the original sounds)


